      "text": "‚ÄúWe're very excited about our new card ‚Äî we're engaging existing customers and reaching new ones with Cardless.‚Äù Sofia Lufinha CCO, TAP Air Portugal ‚ÄúOur collaboration with Cardless gives Simon and our tenants an opportunity to better understand our shoppers and drive incremental sales.‚Äù Michael Thygesen CMO, Simon Property Group Add our dynamic apply button to your app or website. With just a tap, customers can apply for your card using a simple pre-built form that's optimized and rigorously tested across a range of scenarios. Embedded application flow End-to-end card application experience integrated into your product. Pre-filled customer profiles Utilize existing data to speed up time to completion and improve conversion. Screening &amp; underwriting Know your customer, credit checks, and identity verification are built in. Once approved, customers have immediate access to their card, without leaving your app or website. An elegant embedded interface covers payments, transactions, and more‚Ä¶ Embedded experience Display an overview of account information, balance, and recent transactions. Physical and digital cards Digital cards are available immediately. Physical cards are mailed soon after. Account management Embed effortless account management, including card numbers, seamless payments, and Customer Support. An entire credit card experience out of the box We handle partnerships, operational execution, and performance monitoring. Trust our expertise; focus on growth. Drive customer acquisition and loyalty with targeted campaigns and personalized offers. Our Customer Support team is standing by to help throughout the credit card journey. We mitigate threats through advanced risk management tools and fraud detection infrastructure. Stay compliant with industry regulations using our approved solutions, reducing legal and regulatory risks. Ensure the highest level of data security and protect customer data with advanced encryption. Increase customer engagement through compelling rewards programs that incentivize card usage and retention. Utilize your proprietary customer data and our intelligent algorithms and data analytics to increase approvals. Customers interested in a branded credit card Move fast We meticulously navigate the complexities of creating credit cards and continuously improve our platform. Benefit from our expertise, save resources, and deliver a great customer experience. Easy integration Empower your team to accelerate development and streamline the implementation process. Pre-built components Expertly crafted components, delivering an exceptional user experience. Developer support Dedicated developer assistance so your team can build with confidence. Customize to match Configure our pre-built components to match the look and feel your customers know and love, across every screen, detail, and state. Color Looking for something more traditional? Delightful account management available through Cardless. Our app ‚Äî your colors and r",
